{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bde95b4f8a","title":"七绝·呈父亲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"47c5fa7da5","index":0,"year":1910,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"bde95b4f8a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji1","name":"毛泽东全集第1卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e681eef245","type":"paragraph","text":"七绝·呈父亲","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"bde95b4f8a"},{"id":"7fb1eede69","type":"paragraph","text":"（1910年）孩儿立志出乡关团学不成名誉不还。理骨何须桑棒地网","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"bde95b4f8a"},{"id":"c48b4070e3","type":"paragraph","text":"人生无处不青山问[I]七绝，七言绝句的简称。父亲，毛泽东的父亲毛贴昌（1870—1920），字顺生，号良强。生于清代同治九年九月二十一日（1870年10月5日），本于民国八年十二月初三（1920年1月23日），时年50岁。[2]乡关，家乡，故乡。[3]桑粹，古代家宅旁边常裁桑树和特树，看见桑棒，容易引起对父母的怀念，后用作款乡的代称。埋骨何须桑样地，意思是说，人死之后，何必一定要埋在家多。[4]青山，象征祖国山河秀丽。人生无处不青山，意恩是接上句说，祖国到处都是秀丽的河山，可以作为安息的地方。这两句也就是大丈夫志在四方，好男儿四海为家的意思。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"bde95b4f8a"},{"id":"059dd783ac","type":"paragraph","text":"中","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"bde95b4f8a"},{"id":"a703425510","type":"paragraph","text":"S毛泽东的父亲毛胎昌。Bd","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"bde95b4f8a"},{"id":"24f26b7027","type":"paragraph","text":"诚线","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"bde95b4f8a"}],"page":{"id":"70302b6197","publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"bde95b4f8a","start":87,"end":89}}}},"__N_SSG":true}